{"type":"message","id":"be620dd6","parentId":"3286c88b","timestamp":"2026-05-20T02:35:17.256Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have all the information. Let me summarize:\n\n**Voice Issue:**\n1. For receiving/transcribing voice: Need `tools.media.audio.enabled: true` and a transcription provider configured (like deepgram or a Whisper model)\n2. For sending voice: Need `ffmpeg` installed for transcoding to Ogg/Opus\n\nCurrently:\n- `ffmpeg` is NOT installed\n- `tools.media.audio` is not configured (no config shown for it)\n\n**Speed Issue:**\nLooking at the config output again, I see warnings:\n```\n\"warnings\": [\n  { \"path\": \"plugins.entries.feishu\", \"message\": \"plugin feishu: duplicate plugin id detected; global plugin will be overridden by global plugin (/home/halei/.openclaw/npm/node_modules/@openclaw/feishu/dist/index.js)\" },\n  { \"path\": \"plugins.entries.feishu\", \"message\": \"plugin disabled (disabled in config) but config is present\" }\n]\n```\n\nThis suggests there might be a conflict with the feishu plugin. But actually looking at the \"global plugin will be overridden\" message - the local plugin is overriding the global one, not the other way around. And one is disabled.\n\nActually wait - the message says \"plugin disabled (disabled in config) but config is present\". This suggests the config has a feishu plugin entry that's disabled.\n\nBut the main issue might be simpler - the user is comparing 5.4 vs 5.18 speed. Could be:\n1. Model being used (maybe 5.4 used a faster/slower model)\n2. Different settings\n3. Lossless-claw overhead\n4. The compaction/summarization process taking time\n\nLet me provide a clear answer to the user about both issues.","thinkingSignature":"a3eadae26e9b5067e987094df9987db6a25fe095d45e6f3da4df57225196d7bc"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，检查完了。两个问题都找到了原因：\n\n---\n\n## 📌 问题一：语音功能\n\n**接收语音（语音转文字）：**\n- 需要配置 `tools.media.audio` 并启用\n- 需要一个转录 provider（如 Deepgram、Whisper 等）\n- 当前**未配置** `tools.media.audio`\n\n**发送语音（文字转语音）：**\n- 需要 `ffmpeg` 安装进行转码\n- 当前 **ffmpeg 未安装**\n\n**解决方案：**\n1. 安装 ffmpeg：\n   ```bash\n   sudo apt install ffmpeg\n   ```\n2. 配置 `tools.media.audio`（需要转录服务）\n\n---\n\n## 📌 问题二：速度变慢\n\n发现几个可疑点：\n\n1. **ffmpeg 缺失** — 语音转码会失败回退到附件模式（但这不应该影响文字消息速度）\n2. **lossless-claw 开启** — 这个插件会做上下文压缩/摘要，每次都会增加延迟\n3. **streaming 开启** — `streaming: true` 是流式输出，应该更快，但可能跟某些场景不兼容\n\n**建议检查：**\n- 5.4 版本是否也开启了 lossless-claw？\n- 5.4 用的是同一个模型吗？\n- 可以尝试关掉 streaming 试一下：\n  ```bash\n  channels.feishu.streaming = false\n  ```\n\n---\n\n**你希望我帮你做哪个？**\n1. 配置语音（安装 ffmpeg + 启用 audio understanding）\n2. 调整速度相关配置\n3. 两个都搞"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":13314,"output":693,"cacheRead":43702,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57709,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779244498054,"responseId":"065c50d269e7488bb3c2e3c3170352fc"}}
{"type":"message","id":"fed1be56","parentId":"be620dd6","timestamp":"2026-05-20T02:36:18.296Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6fe58306acbcb28bfd1a53a93ae\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-05-20 10:30 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\n你给我发的是文字，没有语音。你检查一下这个新升级的这个5.18版本"}],"timestamp":1779244578278}}
