{"type":"message","id":"2662a9f4","parentId":"4c81033f","timestamp":"2026-05-20T02:42:54.871Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user (HALEI) is saying they just installed WeChat (微信) and that the WeCom (企业微信) CLI messages are not getting replies. They're asking what's going on.\n\nThis is the same WeCom channel - they're saying messages to the WeCom CLI bot are not being responded to.\n\nLet me think about what could cause this:\n1. The WeCom channel might not be properly configured\n2. The bot might not be running\n3. There could be configuration issues\n\nI should check the WeCom configuration and see what's going on. Looking at the earlier config, I saw WeCom mentioned in the plugins but let me check the current WeCom status.\n\nActually, looking at the conversation history, earlier there was a message from \"LeiChao\" via WeCom that I responded to. But the user is saying messages to the WeCom CLI are not getting replies. \n\nWait - looking at the inbound context:\n- channel: \"feishu\" \n- But the user is talking about WeChat (微信) and WeCom (企业微信)\n\nThis seems to be a different channel. Let me check if WeCom is properly configured and running.\n\nActually, looking at the HEARTBEAT.md earlier, I see:\n```\n## /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md\n```\n\nAnd there's mention of wecom in the plugins. Let me check the WeCom configuration.\n\nActually, I should ask for clarification or check the WeCom status. The user says they \"just installed WeChat\" - this could mean they set up a WeChat channel or they installed the WeCom CLI. \n\nLooking at the message metadata again - it's from feishu channel (om_xxx message ID). But the user is asking about WeCom not responding. So they might be asking from Feishu about a separate WeCom issue.\n\nLet me check the WeCom configuration and gateway status to see if WeCom is enabled and running properly.","thinkingSignature":"eb48a9132cfd21615f433db4ba399ae8ff40b827331b2e9abd5cc714cc652e83"},{"type":"text","text":"收到了，但你说的是企业微信（WeCom）那边没回复。让我检查一下 WeCom 的配置和状态：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mbc65owqzmpi_1","name":"gateway","arguments":{"action":"config.get","path":"channels.wecom"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mbc65owqzmpi_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw gateway status 2>&1 | head -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":269,"output":495,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":62266,"totalTokens":63030,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779244958609,"responseId":"065c529f868f238ea5902dd1a7616621"}}
