{"type":"message","id":"7b662b07","parentId":"67b38d4e","timestamp":"2026-05-20T02:43:36.821Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the full configuration. There's both `feishu` and `wecom` channels configured. WeCom is enabled with `botId` and `secret`. So the configuration looks correct.\n\nBut the user is saying WeCom messages are not getting replies. Let me think about what could be wrong:\n\n1. The WeCom plugin might not be properly loaded\n2. The WeCom CLI might need to be restarted after installation\n3. There might be a connection issue\n\nEarlier there was a message from \"LeiChao\" via WeCom that I responded to. But the user is now saying messages aren't getting replies. Maybe the issue is:\n1. The WeCom channel just got set up (user said they \"just installed\" it)\n2. The gateway might need to be restarted to pick up the WeCom configuration\n3. The WeCom plugin might have an issue\n\nLet me check if there are any issues with the WeCom plugin or if it needs a restart.\n\nActually, looking at the config warnings earlier:\n```\n\"warnings\": [\n  { \"path\": \"plugins.entries.feishu\", \"message\": \"plugin feishu: duplicate plugin id detected...\" }\n]\n```\n\nThese are warnings about feishu, not wecom. \n\nBut the gateway is running fine according to the status output. Let me check if there's a wecom plugin issue or if it's properly loaded.\n\nOne possibility: The user just installed the WeCom CLI client. Maybe they need to restart the gateway for the WeCom channel to be properly initialized.\n\nLet me suggest restarting the gateway as a first troubleshooting step.","thinkingSignature":"1f2a7aadc9dc60bb7b14209e5e40c20f64a817e349a7d7ddb8d7fcb7223aaccc"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了！WeCom 确实配置了，而且 `enabled: true`。看起来配置是正常的。\n\n你刚安装完企业微信 CLI，可能需要**重启一下 gateway** 让新安装的组件生效：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n重启完再试试发消息给企业微信 bot，看有没有回复。\n\n如果重启后还是没反应，可能需要检查：\n1. 企业微信机器人的 Webhook 是否正确配置\n2. OpenClaw 的 WeCom 插件是否正常加载\n\n你先重启试试，我等会检查日志看看有没有报错。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":20003,"output":443,"cacheRead":45374,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65820,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779244998873,"responseId":"065c52c7a92eacdf0d65f406acfd4623"}}
