{"type":"message","id":"93dac6d4","parentId":"bd2267cc","timestamp":"2026-05-20T02:45:16.364Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see that the `openclaw-weixin` plugin is present and `enabled: true`. So the plugin is enabled. The user said they successfully scanned and bound their WeChat account.\n\nBut messages aren't getting replies. Let me think about what could be wrong:\n\n1. The plugin is enabled\n2. User did the QR scan login\n3. But messages aren't getting replies\n\nLooking at the config, there's also `wecom-openclaw-plugin` enabled. \n\nWait - the user is saying WeChat messages aren't getting replies. But looking at the plugins, `openclaw-weixin` is enabled. Let me check if there's a channel configuration for weixin/openclaw-weixin.\n\nActually, looking at the channels section earlier, I only saw `feishu` and `wecom`. There's no `openclaw-weixin` or `weixin` channel configured.\n\nBut the plugin being enabled might mean it auto-registers a channel. Let me check if there's a weixin channel in the config.\n\nActually, looking at the docs again:\n> The plugin registers channel id `openclaw-weixin`.\n\nSo the channel id is `openclaw-weixin`. But I don't see it in the `channels` section of the config. Maybe it auto-creates the channel when the plugin is enabled?\n\nLet me check if there's a weixin channel actually running. Maybe the issue is that the gateway needs a restart after the QR login?\n\nOr maybe the issue is that the weixin plugin logs show something. Let me check the logs.\n\nActually, the user said they \"successfully scanned and bound\" - this sounds like they did the QR login. But maybe the gateway wasn't restarted after the login? Or maybe the login didn't complete properly?\n\nLet me suggest checking the logs and restarting the gateway.","thinkingSignature":"6010401c8836f6c9955030d2c83ca0d734bc049d8773c89e90ff94e40304183b"},{"type":"text","text":"微信插件 `openclaw-weixin` 已经**启用**了 ✅\n\n你扫码绑定成功了，那问题可能是：\n\n1. **需要重启 gateway** — 扫码登录后可能需要重启才能让新账号生效\n2. **检查插件是否正常运行** — 看日志有没有报错\n\n先重启 gateway 试试：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n重启后再看日志确认微信插件是否正常加载：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw logs --follow 2>&1 | grep -i weixin\n```\n\n如果日志显示微信插件正常运行，那应该就能收到消息了。你先重启一下试试？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":22302,"output":488,"cacheRead":45374,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68164,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779245101339,"responseId":"065c532d31745a838a8dfdd317f5c2a4"}}
