{"type":"message","id":"d50e615d","parentId":"0b422edc","timestamp":"2026-05-20T02:57:52.078Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying that both personal WeChat and WeCom (Enterprise WeChat) are not working. They're looking at the backend and both show as \"enabled\" or \"开启状态\" (turned on).\n\nLet me check what's actually happening. The user said they looked at the backend and both are in \"开启状态\" (enabled state).\n\nLooking at the conversation context, I see:\n- This message is coming from Feishu (chat_id shows feishu user id)\n- The user is asking about WeChat (个人微信) and WeCom (企业微信) not working\n- Both show as enabled in the backend\n\nLet me think about what could be wrong:\n\n1. For WeChat (`openclaw-weixin`): The plugin is enabled, but is the channel properly configured? Is the WeChat account properly logged in and active?\n\n2. For WeCom (`wecom`): The channel is configured with `enabled: true` and has `botId` and `secret`. But is it actually connected and receiving messages?\n\nThe issue might be:\n- WeChat: The QR login might have expired or the session might not be active\n- WeCom: The connection might not be established properly\n\nLet me check the logs to see if there are any errors. But actually, I don't have direct access to check the logs in real-time from here. Let me suggest some diagnostic steps.\n\nActually, looking at the config again:\n- WeCom has `enabled: true` in channels.wecom\n- WeChat plugin `openclaw-weixin` is enabled\n\nBut just because they're enabled in config doesn't mean they're actually connected and working. The backend showing \"开启状态\" might just mean the config flag is on, not that the actual connection is established.\n\nLet me think about what I can do:\n1. Check if the gateway is running after the restart\n2. Check the logs for errors\n3. Maybe run a diagnostic command\n\nLet me suggest the user check the logs or run a status command to see what's actually happening with these channels.\n\nActually, I should check the gateway status first to make sure it's running after the restart.","thinkingSignature":"c0426028343b2ebb7f3c5ae722d90178ee3f84fd6415298b480025982d8e14b5"},{"type":"text","text":"好，让我检查一下微信和企业微信的实际运行状态。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_53ut8vb7z1i6_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw gateway status 2>&1 | tail -20"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_53ut8vb7z1i6_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw logs 2>&1 | grep -i -E \"(wexin|wechat|wecom|微信|企业微信)\" | tail -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":269,"output":532,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":68199,"totalTokens":69000,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779245853981,"responseId":"065c561ea1e57603791459bcfa701563"}}
