{"type":"message","id":"a223ef20","parentId":"df3c282a","timestamp":"2026-05-20T02:58:04.666Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see:\n\n1. Gateway is running (pid 374503, state active)\n2. There's a warning about `plugins.installs.wecom-openclaw-plugin.spec` and other fields - it says \"config change requires gateway restart (plugins.installs.wecom-openclaw-plugin...)\" - this suggests the wecom plugin was just updated/installed and needs a restart!\n\nBut I just restarted the gateway. The warning says it needs another restart because of the wecom plugin changes.\n\nAlso, I don't see any WeChat/Weixin specific logs in the second command output - it returned empty results (no matches for wexin/wechat/wecom).\n\nLet me check the logs more thoroughly and see what's happening with both channels.","thinkingSignature":"3ea5b93be45a8c6804abf77034b4464cfea9df2c3cc47808e43a8085beb83327"},{"type":"text","text":"Gateway 运行正常 (pid 374503)。但我看到一条重要警告：\n\n> config change requires gateway restart — deferring until... (plugins.installs.wecom-openclaw-plugin.spec...)\n\n这说明 **wecom-openclaw-plugin 插件有更新，需要再重启一次**！\n\n而且日志里没有微信相关的输出，可能微信插件也没有正常加载。让我再检查一下完整的日志：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_eynbx3mcs0zp_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw logs 2>&1 | tail -50"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":23963,"output":260,"cacheRead":45375,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69598,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779245875850,"responseId":"065c5634bff9f89d8b7324939edcaf64"}}
