{"type":"message","id":"54296ae0","parentId":"9e6d07e6","timestamp":"2026-05-20T02:58:24.408Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see some important information from the logs:\n\n1. The WeChat plugin (`openclaw-weixin`) is showing: `2026-05-20T02:38:10.765Z info gateway/channels/openclaw-weixin [compat] Host OpenClaw 2026.5.18 >= 2026.3.22, OK.` - This means the WeChat plugin is loaded and compatible.\n\n2. The gateway was restarted and there's a warning about wecom-openclaw-plugin needing a restart (`config change requires gateway restart (plugins.installs.wecom-openclaw-plugin.spec...)`).\n\n3. There are repeated warnings about `feishu` plugin being duplicated and overridden.\n\n4. The gateway had a shutdown due to the restart I triggered, and there were some pending replies that timed out during shutdown.\n\n5. There's a `lossless-claw` warning about session file not found.\n\n6. There's a warning: `secrets.resolve failed: Secrets runtime snapshot is not active.`\n\nSo the WeChat plugin seems to be loaded (`openclaw-weixin [compat] Host OpenClaw 2026.5.18 >= 2026.3.22, OK.`), but I don't see any indication that it's actually connected and receiving messages.\n\nFor WeCom, there's a config change that requires a restart.\n\nLet me look for more specific information about whether these channels are actually working. The user is saying they sent messages but got no reply.\n\nLet me check if there's anything in the logs about WeCom or WeChat receiving messages. The logs I see don't show any inbound messages to these channels.\n\nI should also check the current gateway status to see if WeCom and WeChat channels are properly connected.\n\nActually, looking more carefully at the log output:\n- WeChat plugin is loaded and compatible\n- WeCom plugin has a pending restart requirement\n\nBut I don't see any logs about receiving messages on either channel. \n\nThe WeChat plugin being loaded and compatible doesn't necessarily mean it's actively connected and processing incoming messages. I need to verify whether these channels are actually receiving and handling messages in real time.","thinkingSignature":"17c562ded3e85db2af624e0b68016f7bfb031eb04482c9e39c3aaf6c8db083c1"},{"type":"text","text":"从日志里我看到几个关键信息：\n\n1. **微信插件已加载**：`gateway/channels/openclaw-weixin [compat] Host OpenClaw 2026.5.18 >= 2026.3.22, OK.`\n2. **企业微信插件有更新，需要重启**：`(plugins.installs.wecom-openclaw-plugin.spec...) — config change requires gateway restart`\n\n但是我没看到任何微信/企业微信收到消息的日志。让我再检查一下这两个插件的实际连接状态：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_uxqhr7sltcth_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw status 2>&1 | head -50"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":26538,"output":570,"cacheRead":45375,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72483,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779245887654,"responseId":"065c56400f002ff45f1d03ea648aa342"}}
