{"type":"message","id":"543058c4","parentId":"258fcb82","timestamp":"2026-05-20T03:00:14.889Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see some important logs! Let me analyze what I see:\n\n1. **WeChat (openclaw-weixin)**:\n   - `Starting Weixin login with bot_type=3`\n   - `NewFetching QR code from: https://ilinkai.weixin.qq.com bot_type=3`\n   - `QR code received` - QR code was received\n   - `waitForWeixinLogin: binded_redirect received, bot already bound sessionKey=f40cddc9a052-im-bot`\n   - `auth.login: bot already connected to this OpenClaw accountId=f40cddc9a052-im-bot`\n\n   So WeChat WAS connected! The bot was already bound to the OpenClaw account. This happened at `2026-05-20T02:29:15`.\n\n2. **WeCom (wecom-openclaw-plugin)**:\n   - Only shows the warning about needing a restart due to config changes\n   - No actual connection logs for WeCom\n\nBut the key issue is that the WeCom plugin has a pending restart requirement. Let me check if after the recent restart, WeCom is now properly loaded.\n\nAlso, I notice that the QR code was fetched and the bot was bound. This suggests the WeChat setup was successful at some point. But was it after the latest restart? The logs show:\n- At 02:28:53 - QR code was received and login started\n- At 02:29:15 - bot already bound (this means the QR was scanned and confirmed)\n- Then later at 02:38:10 and 02:55:45 - just the compatibility check, no new connection logs\n\nSo after the restart, I don't see new WeChat connection logs. This could mean:\n1. The WeChat connection persisted across restarts (good)\n2. Or the WeChat connection was lost and not re-established (bad)\n\nLet me check the latest logs after the restart I just triggered to see if WeCom and WeChat are now properly connected.","thinkingSignature":"b3e71e3f9406d3a7920bc492594e9418b1af650e202997eb87e770ff52e44724"},{"type":"text","text":"现在我看到了一些重要信息！\n\n**微信的日志显示：**\n```\nwaitForWeixinLogin: binded_redirect received, bot already bound\nauth.login: bot already connected to this OpenClaw accountId=f40cddc9a052-im-bot\n```\n\n✅ **微信绑定是成功的** — bot 已经连接到 OpenClaw\n\n**企业微信的日志：**\n```\nconfig change requires gateway restart (plugins.installs.wecom-openclaw-plugin.spec...)\n```\n\n⚠️ **企业微信插件有更新但还未重启生效**\n\n让我看看重启后的日志，确认企业微信是否正常加载了：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8mglmi8yjet8_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw logs 2>&1 | tail -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":32153,"output":574,"cacheRead":45375,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78102,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779245998533,"responseId":"065c56ae6d4c0d6444b7fd06d57d89f6"}}
