{"type":"message","id":"0d2e28f0","parentId":"8cab6884","timestamp":"2026-05-20T03:00:34.585Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the latest logs now. Looking at the timestamps:\n\n- The last restart happened around 02:55:53 (shutdown)\n- New gateway started around 02:56:02\n- Now the current time seems to be around 03:00\n\nBut I don't see any new WeCom or WeChat connection logs after the restart. Let me check if there are any newer logs specifically for these channels.\n\nActually, I notice that the logs show:\n1. `openclaw-weixin [compat] OK` - this is just a compatibility check, not a connection confirmation\n2. No new WeChat connection logs after the restart\n3. No WeCom connection logs at all\n\nThe issue might be that:\n1. WeChat was connected before the restart but after the restart it might need to reconnect\n2. WeCom is still not properly connected/configured\n\nAlso, I see there's a warning: `secrets.resolve failed: Secrets runtime snapshot is not active.` - this could be related to the WeCom configuration if it needs secrets to connect.\n\nLet me think about what to do next:\n1. Wait for the latest logs to come in after the restart\n2. Check if WeChat needs to be re-logged in after restart\n3. Check if WeCom has proper connection status\n\nActually, looking at the WeChat docs earlier:\n> When the Gateway starts, the plugin starts its Weixin monitor for each configured account.\n\nSo when the gateway restarts, the WeChat plugin should automatically reconnect. But maybe the session expired or something.\n\nLet me check the most recent logs after the restart I just triggered to see if there's any new activity.\n\nActually, I just triggered another restart. Let me wait a moment and then check the logs again.","thinkingSignature":"cf76c0064db9d0db1ab3627a4cbf9b9591dbc2ee4411c48930581a4ec09d19c7"},{"type":"text","text":"我看到重启后的日志，但是**没有看到微信和企业微信新的连接日志**。\n\n关键发现：\n1. **微信** — 之前绑定是成功的 (`bot already connected`)，但重启后没有新的连接日志\n2. **企业微信** — 完全没有连接日志，只有 \"需要重启\" 的警告\n\n让我等一下再看最新日志：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vymzzxa6xu7m_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sleep 8 && openclaw logs 2>&1 | tail -20","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":34338,"output":478,"cacheRead":45375,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80191,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779246017941,"responseId":"065c56c27ed7b2600263b4b16ae04389"}}
