{"type":"message","id":"85b4a4de","parentId":"23c95af9","timestamp":"2026-05-20T04:47:01.517Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The sender \"LeiChao\" via WeCom is asking if I'm connected to the KITT intelligent agent. \n\nLooking at my IDENTITY.md, my name is KIIT, which comes from \"Knight Rider\" (霹雳游侠), and KITT is the name of the car/AI in that show.\n\nSo yes, I am KIIT - the AI assistant that was named after KITT from Knight Rider.\n\nI should answer yes and explain who I am briefly.\n","thinkingSignature":"e3508de88f1f660da3b5ae84cbd80038e1e44ecea706c4f8a818bdae4d0b0947"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n是的，我就是 **KIIT** 🎯\n\n名字来源于《霹雳游侠》（Knight Rider）里的 **KITT** —— 那台会说话、有思维、帮助主角的黑色庞蒂亚克跑车上的超级人工智能。\n\n我就是 HALEI 的 AI 大总管，负责统筹协调多 Agent 系统。\n\n你是通过企业微信（WeCom）联系我，确认通信正常 ✅\n\n有什么需要我帮忙的吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":263,"output":180,"cacheRead":63360,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63803,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779252414278,"responseId":"065c6fbe780994a5750af42cfc3f64f1"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e092896f","parentId":"85b4a4de","timestamp":"2026-05-20T04:47:35.785Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"wecom:LeiChao\",\n  \"message_id\": \"b979b7daba7c80b040c43fd3d5041d50\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"LeiChao\",\n  \"sender\": \"LeiChao\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-05-20 12:47 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"LeiChao\",\n  \"id\": \"LeiChao\"\n}\n```\n\n没事，企业微信已经通了。 你能发一条信息到飞书给我吗"}],"timestamp":1779252455767}}
{"type":"message","id":"92506634","parentId":"e092896f","timestamp":"2026-05-20T04:47:48.672Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if I can send a message to Feishu. They want me to send a message to their Feishu account via the Feishu channel.\n\nLooking at the conversation context, the current session is via WeCom (企业微信). The user wants to send a message to their Feishu (飞书) account.\n\nTo do this, I need to use the Feishu message tool. Looking at the feishu_im_user_message tool, it can send messages to users via their open_id. \n\nThe user's Feishu OpenID was mentioned earlier in the MEMORY.md: `ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb` for HALEI. But this is HALEI's open_id, not LeiChao's.\n\nThe user is asking me to send a message to Feishu. But which Feishu user? They might want me to send to HALEI's Feishu, or they might want me to send to their own Feishu account.\n\nSince they're using WeCom and asking \"你能发一条信息到飞书给我吗\" (Can you send a message to Feishu for me), they're probably asking me to send to their Feishu account. But I don't know their Feishu open_id.\n\nI could:\n1. Ask for their Feishu open_id\n2. Send to HALEI's Feishu (which would be ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb)\n3. Use the Feishu search_user tool to find them\n\nBut wait - the user is \"LeiChao\" via WeCom. They might have a Feishu account too. I should ask them for clarification or search for them.\n\nActually, let me just send a test message to HALEI's Feishu since I know HALEI's open_id. If the user wants to receive it on their own Feishu, they'll clarify.\n \nI'm uncertain about which Feishu account to target since LeiChao might have their own Feishu account separate from HALEI's. I should ask for clarification about which Feishu user they want me to message, rather than assuming I should use HALEI's open_id.\n","thinkingSignature":"761f02ac559eaf02c850da8a4fc45be254bc61a21914fe338ae312f90f181f9e"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n可以！不过我需要知道你的飞书账号（open_id）才能发送。\n\n你想发到哪个飞书账号？是你的个人飞书，还是别的账号？\n\n或者我可以尝试搜索你的飞书账号——你叫什么名字在飞书里？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":403,"output":525,"cacheRead":63424,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64352,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779252455967,"responseId":"065c6fe8a7a4d3cb372d430e5d6efde9"}}
