{"type":"message","id":"3421b813","parentId":"71930fda","timestamp":"2026-05-20T06:50:05.208Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is confirming that OpenClaw is running on a cloud server, not their local machine. That's why the browser I open is on the server and they can't see it on their local desktop.\n\nI should acknowledge this and explain what this means for browser control. If they want to see the browser, they would need to either:\n1. Use a remote desktop solution to connect to the server\n2. Install OpenClaw locally on their machine\n3. Have the server stream the screen to them somehow\n\nLet me confirm and explain the situation clearly.","thinkingSignature":"5445a33814fd8d3ae963f147937de2870d1641370bc46620d063b00917b9f61b"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了，OpenClaw 跑在**云端服务器**上，所以浏览器也在服务器上，你本地桌面当然看不到。\n\n这就好比我在一台远程电脑上打开了浏览器，而你在自己电脑前 —— 除非用远程桌面连过去，否则你看不到那个浏览器界面。\n\n**如果你想让浏览器显示在你本地，有几个选择：**\n\n1. **用服务器自带的远程桌面**（RDP/VNC）— 连到服务器去看浏览器\n2. **本地装 OpenClaw** — 这样我可以直接控制你本地的浏览器\n3. **把截图发给你** — 就像刚才那样，我截图为图片发给你看\n\n你现在用的是云端服务器，而且没有配对节点，所以浏览器只能开在服务器端。\n\n你想怎么继续？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":269,"output":267,"cacheRead":87500,"cacheWrite":2013,"totalTokens":90049,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779259794105,"responseId":"065c8c923eab1b253a7b4d18bc657b7a"}}
