{"type":"message","id":"05c135dd","parentId":"d6979182","timestamp":"2026-05-20T06:51:00.904Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I got a screenshot. Let me send this to the user and confirm they can see Baidu via VNC. Then I should ask what they want to do next - search for something, click on links, etc.","thinkingSignature":"70132e6932d5e9826efad5e4c54ac08ffdeacc1a3fe96b4f8efde4a90bf80813"},{"type":"text","text":"百度已打开，你能看到吗？\n\n![百度首页](tool-image.png)\n\n你能看到浏览器里的百度首页了吗？\n\n接下来要做什么？搜索什么内容？点击什么链接？告诉我你来操作。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":45073,"output":87,"cacheRead":45375,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90535,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779259855912,"responseId":"065c8cd04ad585735b4b18f31dc8a9de"}}
