{"type":"message","id":"834ea0f9","parentId":"87e1218d","timestamp":"2026-05-20T06:52:06.492Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying they can't see the browser (百度首页) via VNC. They want to check the openclaw.json configuration regarding the browser.\n\nThey want to see the browser-related configuration in openclaw.json. Let me look at the config for anything related to browser or CDP (Chrome DevTools Protocol) settings.\n\nLooking at the earlier gateway config output, I saw there were some things about browser. Let me search for browser-related config in openclaw.json.","thinkingSignature":"a27df451cac1c70a29bb05ff6849b8a8fafe8b673af1ecd141e6f99f1f6f395b"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，让我查看一下 openclaw.json 里关于浏览器的配置：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sebhawjkger2_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json | python3 -c \"\nimport json,sys\nd=json.load(sys.stdin)\n# Look for browser-related config\nkeys_to_check = ['browser', 'cdp', 'chromium', 'playwright', 'channels']\nfor key in keys_to_check:\n    if key in d:\n        print(f'=== {key} ===')\n        print(json.dumps(d[key], indent=2))\n        print()\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":269,"output":228,"cacheRead":89562,"cacheWrite":718,"totalTokens":90777,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779259919139,"responseId":"065c8d0fdd5563675096c94f8706b74b"}}
