{"type":"message","id":"9eb30131","parentId":"51325207","timestamp":"2026-05-20T06:55:55.638Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to log in to TikTok Shop backend (后套 means backend). They're sending from the Feishu channel (sender_id ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb is HALEI).\n\nThey want me to help them log in to TikTok Shop's seller/backend portal. The URL for TikTok Shop seller center is typically something like https://seller.tiktok.com or https://affiliate.tiktok.com or similar.\n\nLet me navigate to TikTok Shop seller backend using the browser. I should first navigate to the TikTok Shop login page.\n","thinkingSignature":"b2c4ecb6beeeee35fa437569b5833773ccbd9bcfb2ada2c094c28de231062db8"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好的，我打开 TikTok Shop 后台。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_93yg26kkcf7q_1","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"navigate","targetId":"8F7138AA0DDEF8CF511945352639D66F","url":"https://seller.tiktok.com"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":15040,"output":199,"cacheRead":70456,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85695,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779260144071,"responseId":"065c8df0c9425af1d1ecf09078d4fd40"}}
