{"type":"message","id":"75d90c55","parentId":"e74ce1ef","timestamp":"2026-05-20T06:56:25.955Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No browser, security, policy settings found in the config. The navigation was blocked. This might be a built-in safety policy in OpenClaw that blocks certain domains. Let me try with web_search or web_fetch instead to understand what the user is trying to do.\n\nActually, the user wants to log in to TikTok Shop backend. The navigation is blocked. Maybe I need to check the browser-automation skill to see if there's a way to allow certain domains.\n\nBut actually, thinking about this more carefully - TikTok Shop might have strict anti-bot measures that would detect and block headless Chrome. Also, logging into a commercial platform like TikTok Shop might require additional verification (2FA, phone verification, etc.) that could be problematic.\n\nI should explain the situation and see what the user wants to do specifically. Maybe they want to do something specific on TikTok Shop backend that I can help with.\n","thinkingSignature":"e9ee9fa38ad89c4550d73f0dd3ccd397eb332f6f262d5cc3cabc256c65e5aaeb"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n导航被阻止了，可能是 OpenClaw 的安全策略限制了某些域名。\n\n另外要注意：**TikTok Shop 后台对自动化工具管控很严**，headless Chrome 很可能被检测为机器人并被封号或要求验证。\n\n**你想在 TikTok Shop 后台做什么？**\n\n- 商品上架/编辑？\n- 订单查看？\n- 数据分析？\n- 其他操作？\n\n告诉我具体需求，我评估一下可行性，再决定怎么操作。有些平台对自动化登录有限制，需要换其他方式。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4083,"output":286,"cacheRead":81646,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86015,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779260168320,"responseId":"065c8e08a8c0bb7baecfff11b9a22aac"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7a96c86e","parentId":"75d90c55","timestamp":"2026-05-20T06:57:26.970Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6fe1fbc97cb8c2c3100b268e0e7\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-05-20 14:57 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\n一个免登录链接， 页面有图片，无头模式下能获取到吗"}],"timestamp":1779260246952}}
