{"type":"message","id":"f0953a65","parentId":"55ddbda7","timestamp":"2026-05-20T06:58:00.954Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about a non-login link (免登录链接) that has images. They want to know if headless Chrome can get/access the images on the page.\n\nThe answer is yes - headless Chrome can access and load images just like a normal browser. The issue with headless mode is mainly about:\n1. No visible UI (you can't see it)\n2. Some sites detect and block headless browsers\n3. CAPTCHAs and 2FA can be problematic\n\nBut for simply accessing and loading images on a page that doesn't require login - headless Chrome can absolutely do that. It renders the full page including images.\n\nSo the user is asking a different question now - they're not trying to log in, they have a direct link that doesn't require login, and the page has images. They just want to know if headless Chrome can access those images.\n\nThe answer is yes - headless Chrome can access and load images just fine. The CDP (Chrome DevTools Protocol) that OpenClaw uses can take screenshots of the page which would include the images, or we could extract the image URLs from the page.\n\nLet me explain this clearly.\n","thinkingSignature":"b2443ebf87b4a5a1475bf12bfd38ed70980a46cda69de4ae1aa9bdf5894fa20d"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**可以的！** 无头模式能正常加载页面和图片。\n\n无头 Chrome 的问题是\"看不到界面\"，不是\"不能加载内容\"。它可以：\n\n✅ 加载所有图片（和其他资源）\n✅ 执行 JavaScript\n✅ 渲染完整页面\n✅ 截图获取页面内容\n✅ 提取图片链接\n\n只要你那个免登录链接不需要验证码或人机验证，直接访问就行。\n\n要我试试打开那个链接并截图吗？把链接发给我。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":85733,"output":333,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86322,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779260247172,"responseId":"065c8e5715bb1f12483efb097568d985"}}
