{"type":"message","id":"8e3f68c9","parentId":"83d07994","timestamp":"2026-05-20T07:14:09.447Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the screenshot! It's the OpenClaw Infrastructure settings page. I can see:\n\n1. Under \"KITT-AGI\" project, \"Browser\" category is selected\n2. There's a notification showing one unsaved change: updating `browser` from `undefined` to `{\"actionTimeoutMs\": -1}`\n3. Below that I can see \"Remote CDP Timeout\" and \"Browser Snapshot Defaults\" settings\n4. There's a \"Save\" button\n\nThe user is showing me that there's a Browser setting in the Infrastructure section and it's currently showing `undefined`. There's an unsaved change to set it to `{\"actionTimeoutMs\": -1}`.\n\nBut wait - the user said \"browser 没启动\" (browser not started). Looking at the screenshot more carefully, I think the issue is that the Browser service in the Infrastructure settings is not enabled or running.\n\nThe notification says \"updating `browser` from `undefined` to `{\"actionTimeoutMs\": -1}`\" - this suggests the browser config is being updated but not saved. The user might need to click Save to apply this change, which would then start the browser service.\n\nBut actually, looking at the settings, it seems like `browser` is currently `undefined` which means the browser service might not be configured/enabled. Setting it to `{\"actionTimeoutMs\": -1}` is just a configuration change, not enabling the browser itself.\n\nI should help the user understand what they need to do. They probably need to save this configuration to enable the browser service, or there might be a separate \"start\" or \"enable\" option for the browser.\n\nLet me look at what options are available. The screenshot shows the Browser section under Infrastructure. It seems like the browser config is being shown but might not be enabled.\n\nActually, I think I need to see more of the interface. But based on what I can see, the user should:\n1. Click Save to save the `{\"actionTimeoutMs\": -1}` configuration\n2. After saving, the browser service might start automatically, or there might be a separate start button\n\nLet me respond to the user and guide them to save the configuration first.\n","thinkingSignature":"d390a470299e541e7fc2e08b02d2ac30db29a9560e7855176d98db6805826b32"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n看到了！这是 OpenClaw 的 Infrastructure 设置页面，Browser 配置当前是 `undefined`。\n\n你显示有一条未保存的更改：`browser` → `{\"actionTimeoutMs\": -1}`\n\n**先点击 Save 保存这个配置**，然后告诉我保存后发生了什么。\n\n保存后如果 Browser 还是没启动，可能需要开启 Browser MCP 或者相关服务。你先保存试试，我看到结果再帮你下一步操作。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":88144,"output":529,"cacheRead":3072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91745,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779261221126,"responseId":"065c92250d01360a490755a876c6c073"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6c01e10a","parentId":"8e3f68c9","timestamp":"2026-05-20T07:15:59.316Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6fe1b499f8a8c23ebf4ebdd7b5d\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-05-20 15:15 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\n我的意思是， 是不是因为这个才没打开可视化浏览器，"}],"timestamp":1779261359194}}
