{"type":"message","id":"e0d7b1bf","parentId":"223be383","timestamp":"2026-05-20T07:46:17.552Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to execute the configuration change. They want `headless: false` so the browser will be visible on their VNC desktop. Let me patch the browser config and then restart the gateway.\n\nI need to:\n1. Set `browser.headless: false`\n2. Make sure the browser will connect to the correct display (:1 where VNC is)\n3. Restart the gateway\n4. Then open a new browser and it should be visible on VNC\n\nLet me do the config patch.\n","thinkingSignature":"e706b162dc652404836b1a3720c7e69d0285724e658e1c78df8612d427fd33a8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_y16u1wym6xhm_1","name":"gateway","arguments":{"action":"config.patch","note":"关闭 headless 模式，让浏览器显示在 VNC 桌面上","raw":"{\"browser\": {\"headless\": false, \"defaultProfile\": \"user\", \"profiles\": {\"work\": {\"cdpPort\": 18801, \"color\": \"#3B82F6\"}, \"personal\": {\"cdpPort\": 18802, \"color\": \"#10B981\"}}}}"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5719,"output":223,"cacheRead":92048,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97990,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779263167089,"responseId":"065c99bff6b4ad6ac3d912df136d0de1"}}
