{"type":"message","id":"86b30cfe","parentId":"41b20465","timestamp":"2026-05-20T07:48:23.142Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to:\n1. Open two browser profiles that I just configured (work and personal)\n2. One visits Baidu (百度)\n3. One visits QQ (腾讯)\n4. Use the colors I configured\n\nThe profiles are:\n- work: cdpPort 18801, color \"#3B82F6\"\n- personal: cdpPort 18802, color \"#10B981\"\n\nI need to open two separate browser tabs/instances. The browser tool should be able to use different profiles. Let me check if I can specify a profile when opening a browser.\n\nFirst, let me check the current browser status to see what profiles are available and then try to open two browsers with different profiles.\n","thinkingSignature":"766e626ff41bc89becbe3389d685be8fe4d7c5a482080ce305c949fe6935983a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wpyt2zb31gqw_1","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"status"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5498,"output":171,"cacheRead":92976,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98645,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779263287666,"responseId":"065c9a3865d209faa43ed22f39117017"}}
